rdbreader extracts files from Funcom RDB archives.  It is meant to be run in
the directory containing the RDB directory.  Output directory is set in
config.h, where you can also select which types of files to extract.

fctxconverter attemps to convert Funcom's texture container format back into
DDS.

lipreader extracts audio data from LIP files.

Tested in VS2012 and on Debian squeeze.